The task1, task2, task3 folders each contain their own makefile, as well as the
test files used in the tests for each task.



task1
	task1.cpp
	makefile
	t1_5lines.txt		// 5 lines
	t1_10lines.txt		// 10 lines
	t1_15lines.txt		// 15 lines

task2
	task2.cpp
	makefile
	t2_append.txt		// existing file - append output
	t2_create.txt		// created file

task3
	task3.cpp			// main 
	t3_class.cpp		// class definitions
	t3_class.h			// class declarations
	makefile
	t3_input.txt		// input test file (with some values missing but correct number of products)
	t3_empty.txt		// empty file for input
